ue\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></header><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-[1440px] items-start\"><aside class=\"hidden w-64 shrink-0 md:block lg:w-72\"><div class=\"sticky top-16 h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] overflow-y-auto border-r border-white/5 bg-[#090a0a] py-8 pr-6 pl-6 custom-scrollbar\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8\"><div><h4 class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500\">Get started</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1 my-0 list-none pl-0\"><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/introduction\">Introduction</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500\">Architecture &amp; Systems</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1 my-0 list-none pl-0\"><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/architecture\">Architecture</a></li><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/rules-engine\">Rules Engine</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500\">Product Features</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1 my-0 list-none pl-0\"><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/core-features/builder\">Visual Builder</a></li><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/core-features/runtime\">Runtime Engine</a></li><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/core-features/copy\">Copy Trading</a></li><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/core-features/copilot\">AI Copilot</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500\">References</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1 my-0 list-none pl-0\"><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors bg-[#dce85d]/10 text-[#dce85d] font-medium\" href=\"/docs/api-reference\">API Reference</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-neutral-500\">Vision</h4><ul class=\"space-y-1 my-0 list-none pl-0\"><li><a class=\"block rounded-md px-3 py-2 text-sm transition-colors text-neutral-400 hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\" href=\"/docs/roadmap\">Roadmap</a></li></ul></div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-16\"><div class=\"pb-24 pt-10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)\"><div class=\"mb-10 space-y-4\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white\">API Reference</h1><p class=\"text-lg leading-7 text-neutral-400\">FastAPI service endpoints and routing structures.</p></div><div class=\"[&amp;&gt;h2]:scroll-mt-24 [&amp;&gt;h2]:text-2xl [&amp;&gt;h2]:font-semibold [&amp;&gt;h2]:tracking-tight [&amp;&gt;h2]:text-white [&amp;&gt;h2]:mt-12 [&amp;&gt;h2]:mb-8 [&amp;&gt;h2]:border-b [&amp;&gt;h2]:border-white/10 [&amp;&gt;h2]:pb-4 [&amp;&gt;h3]:scroll-mt-24 [&amp;&gt;h3]:text-xl [&amp;&gt;h3]:font-semibold [&amp;&gt;h3]:tracking-tight [&amp;&gt;h3]:text-white [&amp;&gt;h3]:mt-10 [&amp;&gt;h3]:mb-4 [&amp;&gt;p]:text-neutral-300 [&amp;&gt;p]:leading-7 [&amp;&gt;p:not(:last-child)]:mb-6 [&amp;&gt;ul]:text-neutral-300 [&amp;&gt;ul]:list-disc [&amp;&gt;ul]:pl-6 [&amp;&gt;ul]:mb-6 [&amp;&gt;ul&gt;li]:mb-2 [&amp;&gt;ol]:text-neutral-300 [&amp;&gt;ol]:list-decimal [&amp;&gt;ol]:pl-6 [&amp;&gt;ol]:mb-6 [&amp;&gt;ol&gt;li]:mb-2 [&amp;_a]:text-[#dce85d] [&amp;_a]:transition-colors hover:[&amp;_a]:underline [&amp;_strong]:text-white w-full max-w-none\"><div class=\"my-6 flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border p-5 border-[#dce85d]/20 bg-[#dce85d]/5 text-neutral-100\"><div class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#dce85d]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg></div><div><h5 class=\"mb-1 font-semibold text-[#dce85d]\">Protected Architecture</h5><div class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-300\">Vega uses a RESTful backend written in FastAPI (Python 3.11+). All endpoints are protected by Privy JWT validation via Middleware, resolving to the authenticated user&#x27;s wallet automatically.</div></div></div><h2>Authentication and Authorization</h2><div class=\"my-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#000000]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-terminal h-4 w-4 text-neutral-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19h8\"></path><path d=\"m4 17 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400\">http</span></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4\"><pre class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-400 font-mono\"><code>GET  /api/sodex/authorize         # Check authorization status\nPOST /api/sodex/authorize/start   # Initiate delegated wallet auth\nPOST /api/sodex/authorize/activate # Complete activation</code></pre></div></div><h2>Bot Builder and Runtime</h2><div class=\"my-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#000000]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-terminal h-4 w-4 text-neutral-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19h8\"></path><path d=\"m4 17 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400\">http</span></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4\"><pre class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-400 font-mono\"><code>GET   /api/bots                      # List all bots owned by user\nPOST  /api/bots                      # Create a new bot definition\nGET   /api/bots/{bot_id}             # Get bot details and runtime state\nPATCH /api/bots/{bot_id}             # Update bot configuration\nPOST  /api/bots/{bot_id}/validate    # Validate bot rules\nPOST  /api/bots/{bot_id}/deploy      # Deploy bot to start live execution\nPOST  /api/bots/{bot_id}/pause       # Pause runtime\nPOST  /api/bots/{bot_id}/resume      # Resume runtime\nPOST  /api/bots/{bot_id}/stop        # Permanently stop\nGET   /api/bots/{bot_id}/events      # List execution event logs</code></pre></div></div><h2>Copy Trading</h2><div class=\"my-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#000000]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-terminal h-4 w-4 text-neutral-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19h8\"></path><path d=\"m4 17 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400\">http</span></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4\"><pre class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-400 font-mono\"><code>POST   /api/bots/{id}/copy/preview   # Preview mirror relationship\nPOST   /api/bots/{id}/copy/mirror    # Activate live mirroring\nPOST   /api/bots/{id}/copy/clone     # Clone bot configuration\nPATCH  /api/copy/{id}                # Update relationship\nDELETE /api/copy/{id}                # Deactivate relationship</code></pre></div></div><h2>Realtime Streaming</h2><div class=\"my-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-[#000000]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-4 py-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-terminal h-4 w-4 text-neutral-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 19h8\"></path><path d=\"m4 17 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400\">http</span></div></div><div class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4\"><pre class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-emerald-400 font-mono\"><code>GET /api/stream/bots/{runtime_id}    # SSE stream for bot runtime events\nGET /api/stream/leaderboard/bots      # SSE stream for leaderboard updates\nGET /api/stream/user/{user_id}       # SSE stream for user-level events</code></pre></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-64 shrink-0 xl:block 2xl:w-72 pr-6\"></aside></div></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-768b348ffe7363e7.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[22564,[\\\"6229\\\",\\\"static/chunks/881ff0cd-67cd6e3f1a4ce407.js\\\",\\\"7148\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7148-ef066f02ea3dccee.js\\\",\\\"7336\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7336-446a7c1f56832b0f.js\\\",\\\"8366\\\",\\\"static/chunks/8366-300b1eafae40d2bc.js\\\